{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2300678_translations":{"at":1772973282850,"data":{"id":2300678,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zhao Zhi Wei, English name Eden also known simply as Zhiwei, is a Chinese actor, singer, and dancer. He was a member of the Taiwanese boyband SpeXial from 2016 to 2017.\n\nZhao was born in Lanzhou, Gansu. He attended and graduated from Shanghai Theater Academy and performed as a dancer for ten years. Throughout the years, he participated in many national and international dance competitions and has also acted as a choreographer. Before graduating, the academy wanted Zhao to stay and serve as a teacher, but he was diagnosed with a serious knee injury that forced him to quit dancing. After that, he decided to become an actor and starred in his first television series, KO One Re-member, in 2016 and officially entered the entertainment industry.\n\nOn July 14 of the same year, Zhao became a member of the Taiwanese boyband SpeXial and participated in the recording of their 4th album, Boyz on Fire. Along with several of his bandmates, he participated in the costume drama series Men with Sword.\n\nOn March 20, 2017, Zhao announced that he was going to leave SpeXial for unspecified reasons. His departure took place three days later, on March 23, less than a year after joining the group. He was also the second member to leave SpeXial after his bandmate Simon, who left the group on February 2, 2017. Zhao signed with Huace Media following his departure to embark on his acting activities.","name":"Zhao Zhiwei","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"赵志伟，1994年8月8日出生于甘肃兰州，中国内地男演员、歌手，毕业于上海戏剧学院。\n\n2016年，主演个人首部电视剧《终极一班4》而正式进入演艺圈；同年7月19日，加入男子演唱团体SpeXial，之后随SpeXial发布专辑《Boyz On Fire》；同年8月14日，主演的古装偶像剧《刺客列传》在搜狐视频上线。2017年，主演运动题材励志剧《蔚蓝50米》；同年12月，出演根据张皓宸同名小说改编的舞台剧《我与世界只差一个你》 。2018年3月，参演都市青春情感剧《我只喜欢你》；8月10日，参演的喜剧电影《爱情公寓》在全国公映。","name":"赵志伟","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"趙志偉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Triệu Chí Vỹ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжао Чжи Вэй","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"조지위","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"趙志偉，1994 年 8 月 8 日出生於甘肅蘭州，中國內地男演員、歌手，畢業於上海戲劇學院。\n\n2016 年，主演個人首部電視劇《終極一班 4》而正式進入演藝圈；同年 7 月 19 日，加入男子演唱團體 SpeXial，之後隨 SpeXial 發佈專輯《Boyz On Fire》；同年 8 月 14 日，主演的古裝偶像劇《刺客列傳》在搜狐視頻上線。2017 年，主演運動題材勵志劇《蔚藍 50 米》；同年 12 月，出演根據張皓宸同名小説改編的舞台劇《我與世界只差一個你》 。2018 年 3 月，參演都市青春情感劇《我只喜歡你》；8 月 10 日，參演的喜劇電影《愛情公寓》在全國公映。","name":"趙志偉","primary":false}}]}},"person_3206201_translations":{"at":1773039163508,"data":{"id":3206201,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Brent Downs","primary":true}}]}},"person_1384976_translations":{"at":1773146659845,"data":{"id":1384976,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Thea Sofie Loch Næss (born November 26, 1996) is a Norwegian actress known for her performances in film and television. She was born in Kristiansand, Norway, and started acting at the age of 8.\n\nShe gained recognition for her leading role in One Night in Oslo (2014) and later starred in The Last King (2016) as Kristina of Norway. In 2018, she played the villain Skade in the third season of The Last Kingdom on Netflix. More recently, she portrayed Marianne Ihlen in the 2024 biographical mini-series So Long, Marianne, which explores the life of Leonard Cohen’s muse.\n\nBeyond acting, she studied drama at Hartvig Nissens School in Oslo and has appeared in various Norwegian and international productions.","name":"Thea Sofie Loch Næss","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"NO","iso_639_1":"no","name":"Norsk","english_name":"Norwegian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Thea Sofie Loch Næss","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"西娅·索菲·内丝","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"西婭·索菲·內絲","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Теа Соф'є Лок Несс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Норвежская актриса. Выросла в Осло. С детства мечтала связать свою жизнь с актёрством. Играла небольшие роли в театре. В 2014 году дебютировала в кино. Loch — фамилия отца, Næss — фамилия матери Теа Софи.","name":"Теа Софи Лох Несс","primary":false}}]}},"person_4413442_translations":{"at":1773146660342,"data":{"id":4413442,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mohammed Bilal Khan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mohammed Bilal Khan","primary":true}}]}},"movie_632464_credits":{"at":1773319434530,"data":{"id":632464,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2104877,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Valentina Karoleva","original_name":"Valentina Karoleva","popularity":0.3852,"profile_path":"/noCUKmkcd4TjnthC47N1FhDIQfV.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Vesela","credit_id":"5d8354b79e45860272941944","order":0},{"adul